{
  "stem": "9878.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Here I sent a letter to Brooklyn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he got himself the address, and he's writing to his grandfather.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Little did I realize that America is so easy to get an address that, like this, you pick up a telephone, you call.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My family's name, my mother's name is [INAUDIBLE] Nobody-- any [INAUDIBLE] is my relative.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Any [INAUDIBLE] in the book-- there's very few-- is my relatives.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to him, could you write to your grandfather?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know my uncle lives in Brooklyn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said Brooklyn a little town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because maybe you'll find my uncle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His name is Sam [INAUDIBLE] and I have a tante, Rose Lindeman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But Lindeman didn't have a telephone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] had a telephone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So lo and behold, he says to me, give me 300 rubles. 300 rubles is two months'-- two months' labor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I made 150 rubles a month, working very hard as a fireman to fire the fires of the tanks, to meld the steel.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I worked like a son of a gun then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, he needed the money to support his habit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I don't want to belittle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, let him rest in peace where he is, or be wherever he is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And lo and behold, I sit down and write 16 pages, written tears and blood, telling what has happened to my family, what happened the way they made them go down, the way they made the women to undress, they way they beat them.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my grandparents was their father and mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father-- my grandparents was their father and mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother and my sister made everybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I send away a letter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Three months later, the letter comes back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The letter was red stamped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The letter was not accepted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "His letter is gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
